  "description": "Minecraft resource pack to make the all the bush variants a bit \"bushier\"!",
  "body": "<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2743714708869b54242d757a279aec3e6f6c4bd9_0.webp\">\n</center>\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/ASpjFDwX\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/384923d44f1049b05e3177bd0a6065876f2cab30.png\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://x.com/MegaNecra\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/35eb2f8fb4a3356c7a5ee6b9a93cf2b83a55a765.png\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://vgen.co/MegaNecra\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/aae4e3ef14436970a34f10a0e4780c3f8bfbc5f0.png\">\n  </a>\n</center>\n\n<hr>\n\n\n<center>\nThis resource pack is fairly simple. It makes the bushes officially added in 1.21.5 and the Sweet Berry Bushes a bit <b>bushier</b> by adding a custom model that does just that.\n</center>\n\n<hr>\n\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/32b58a861ff84c2498e142fd0ba28c23e2718969.webp\">\n</center>\n\n<hr>\n\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4a852ac60575b82b18157009ecc7f714d15ab94e.png\">\n</center>\n  \n<hr>\n\n- Add connected texture support to connect the bushes when placed next to eachother. (Currently trying to get it working the way I want.)\n\n<hr>\n\n<center>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d9618da9f24df34a0e38c0f3d71dda4d49e49df.png\">\n</center>\n  \n<hr>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/nny6zZ5jLfY\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n### Shoutout to [demonjoeTV](https://modrinth.com/user/demonjoeTV) for including this pack in his YouTube Short and in the video above!\n[Click here to see the short!](https://www.youtube.com/shorts/_NjpefHIuR0)\n\n<center>\n<b>Check out my other packs!</b>\n</center>\n  \n<hr>\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/torchier-torches-mn\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6a8597445482bde9f862e56f1be258e07c98a5b4.png\">\n  </a>\n</center>\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/pointier_spears\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8d301d62c6c5a651ccae9c7359a77f4af3c7a2b6.png\">\n  </a>\n</center>\n\n<hr>\n\n## External Links\n\n### Looking for a Minecraft Skin or a custom Minecraft model? \n**[Click here](https://vgen.co/MegaNecra) to check out my VGen and commission me!** \n\n### Have any thoughts on how I could improve this pack or just want to join my community?\n**Join my [Discord](https://discord.gg/ASpjFDwX)!**",
